PrecisAppointment of PHILIPPE BEAULNE as High Commissioner for Canada to the Republic of Sierra Leone, with residence in Conakry; JEAN-PIERRE BOLDUC as Ambassador of Canada to the Togolese Republic, with residence in Accra; JOSEPH CARON as Ambassador of Canada to the Democratic People's Republic of Korea and to Mongolia, with residence in Beijing; JOHN DONAGHY as High Commissioner for Canada to Samoa, with residence in Wellington; JEAN T. FOURNIER as High Commissioner for Canada to Papua New Guinea, with residence in Canberra; EMILE GAUVREAU as Ambassador of Canada to the Republic of Benin, with residence in Abidjan; LOUISE LÉGER as Ambassador of Canada to the Republic of Honduras and to the Republic of Nicaragua, with residence in San José; SERGE MARCOUX as Ambassador of Canada to the Republic of Suriname, with residence in Georgetown; DAVID STOCKWELL as High Commissioner for Canada to the Republic of Malawi, with residence in Lusaka; and DENIS THIBAULT as Ambassador of Canada to the Republic of Cape Verde and to the Islamic Republic of Mauritania, with residence in Dakar.
